summary: Modifies every argonian in the game to be more raptor-like in appearance
descriptionHtml:
Similar to my Nicer-Looking Khajiits mod, this modifies the face structure of every argonian in the game to give them more of a raptor-like appearance. 

All work has been done with sliders, so it should not interfere with any texture mods or anything like that. 

Until the day where new meshes are made for Argonian heads, this is just about the next best thing.
author: BeakieHelmet
